cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with visual perception of 3D geometry. It may also belong to Robotics (cs.RO) as autonomous systems require robust geometry perception. Additionally, the paper introduces a novel framework that integrates semantic information, which may fall under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper may also belong to Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) as it deals with semantic information integration.
